{"type":"message","id":"f91adf9b","parentId":"7a4ecf66","timestamp":"2026-03-26T05:50:46.905Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" asks about \"跨境电商团队，选品agent 创建好了吗\". Likely they expect an agent for selection. Not present. Need to create a new skill? Probably need to inform not yet created. Suggest creating.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"我在本地的技能目录里目前只有 Feishu 官方提供的几个工具（Bitable、Bot‑Manager、Calendar、任务、文档 等），还没有专门针对跨境电商选品的 Agent。\n\n如果您需要一个 **选品 Agent**，我们可以现在就把它创建为一个新的 Skill（放在 `~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/selection‑agent/`），随后再按照您的业务流程编写对应的实现代码或调用已有的 Feishu 接口。\n\n请告诉我：\n\n1. **选品 Agent 需要具备哪些功能**（例如：查询商品库、生成选品报告、推送到 Feishu 表格、定时提醒等）；\n2. 您希望它使用哪种触发方式（手动指令、定时任务、消息关键词）；\n3. 是否已有相关的 API 文档或数据源（比如商品库 CSV、数据库、第三方平台）；\n\n有了这些信息，我就能帮您快速搭建并部署选品 Agent。祝您跨境电商业务顺利！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":16510,"output":343,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16853,"cost":{"input":-16510,"output":-343,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-16853}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774504243079}}
